snippet.title: Madden 24 Franchise Deep Dive & Mini-Games
snippet.description:
Go inside Madden NFL 24 with a deep dive into Franchise mode updates. 
Pre-order now: http://x.ea.com/76877
—
Learn about Franchise progression in Madden 24 through training camp, all-new mini-games, and improvements to coach talent trees. Check out new team-building improvements to trades, free agency contracts, and expanded draft class generators; and play the way you want with new Franchise relocation options and commissioner tools.

Madden NFL 24 is available worldwide August 18, 2023

#madden24
